TopicTitle: Found lying on the road : IKCOSS Station now with solar panels.

Articles.Content:
I've been required (before the First-But-Not-Last-Forums-Jebargeddon) to add a part to the IKCOSS station (does the last S is for "station" already ?), so I did. Took my time, but it now has nice and big solar panels. And a 4 mins accelerated video showing how it was a pain to bring it up there.

But I don't know what to do with it now... Someone around to claim the property of this ?
